snippet: The former Pro Bowl tight end Kellen Winslow, seeking to rejuvenate his career after a balky right knee injury, will try out for the Jets at their minicamp this week.
abstract: Former Pro Bowl tight end Kellen Winslow, seeking to rejuvenate his career after a balky right knee injury, will try out for New York Jets at minicamp.
lead_paragraph: The former Pro Bowl tight end Kellen Winslow, seeking to rejuvenate his career after a balky right knee injury, will try out for the Jets at their minicamp this week.
